Queen Bey is now the owner of a church. The church which is located in New Orleans is reported to be 7,500 sq.ft. According to TMZ, the church building dates back to over a 100 years old and was put at $850,000 (N306,000,000). Beyonces church. Photo credit: TMZ The church building has not been in use for a while now because of its members’ deaths. Read More: Church In San Francisco Organises ‘Beyonce Mass’ Time will tell what she will use the church for. An actual Beyonce Mass maybe?